Jodie Barden has two daughters with Cockayne Syndrome . 
  Ella, eight and Chloe, one, have a life expectancy of just 12 because of the rare genetic disorder . 
  It causes premature ageing, underdeveloped nervous system and a small head . 
  Mrs Barden is forced to plan both daughters' funerals as neither will live to adulthood . 
  She was diagnosed with the disease in 2012 and has a one-in-four chance of surviving . 
  She has already made arrangements for their funerals . 
 